'''詹姆士·戴森'''爵士，[[大英帝國勳章|CBE]] [[皇家工程院|FREng]]<ref name="raeng1">{{cite web|title=List of Fellows|url=http://www.raeng.org.uk/about-us/people-council-committees/the-fellowship/list-of-fellows|access-date=2015-07-18|archive-date=2016-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160608094405/http://www.raeng.org.uk/about-us/people-council-committees/the-fellowship/list-of-fellows|dead-url=no}}</ref> [[皇家学会|FRS]]（{{lang-en|Sir '''James Dyson'''}}，{{bd|1947年|5月2日}}），英國[[發明家|發明家]]、[[工业设计|工業設計師]]，以及[[戴森_(公司)|戴森公司]]創辦人。他最著名的發明是靠著[[旋風分離|旋風分離]]原理運作的雙氣旋無袋式[[吸塵機|吸塵機]]。根據{{tsl|en|Sunday Times Rich List 2013|2013年星期日泰晤士報富豪榜}}，他的資產淨值高達三十億英鎊<ref name=whoswho/><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.itv.com/news/west/update/2013-04-19/inventor-dyson-tops-south-west-rich-list/ |work=ITV |title=Inventor Dyson tops south west rich list |accessdate=20 June 2013 |archive-date=2018-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181016125849/http://www.itv.com/news/west/update/2013-04-19/inventor-dyson-tops-south-west-rich-list/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=autobiography>{{cite book | year = 1997 | first = James | last = Dyson | title = Against The Odds: An Autobiography | url = https://archive.org/details/againstoddsautob0000dyso | author2-link = Giles Coren | first2 = Giles | last2 = Coren | isbn = 0-7528-0981-4}}</ref>。

